## Recursive Merge

If either tree is null, return the other. Otherwise, add the values together and recursively merge left and right children.

```js
function mergeTwoBinaryTrees(t1, t2) {
  if (!t1) return t2;
  if (!t2) return t1;
  t1.val += t2.val;
  t1.left = mergeTwoBinaryTrees(t1.left, t2.left);
  t1.right = mergeTwoBinaryTrees(t1.right, t2.right);
  return t1;
}
```

