## 2D Prefix Sum

Precompute a 2D prefix sum. For each query, use inclusion-exclusion to compute the region sum in O(1).

```js
function rangeSumQuery2dImmutable(matrix, row1, col1, row2, col2) {
  const m = matrix.length, n = matrix[0].length;
